{"data":{"wpPage":{"title":"About","uri":"/about/","nodeType":"Page","seo":{"title":"About | The PM Group","metaDesc":"","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","metaRobotsNoindex":"index","opengraphTitle":"About | The PM Group","opengraphDescription":"","opengraphImage":null,"twitterTitle":"","twitterDescription":"","twitterImage":null,"canonical":"/about/","cornerstone":false,"schema":{"articleType":[],"pageType":["WebPage"],"raw":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@graph\":[{\"@type\":\"WebSite\",\"@id\":\"/#website\",\"url\":\"/\",\"name\":\"The PM Group\",\"description\":\"San Antonio\\u2019s Largest Advertising and Marketing Agency\",\"potentialAction\":[{\"@type\":\"SearchAction\",\"target\":{\"@type\":\"EntryPoint\",\"urlTemplate\":\"/?s={search_term_string}\"},\"query-input\":\"required name=search_term_string\"}],\"inLanguage\":\"en-US\"},{\"@type\":\"WebPage\",\"@id\":\"/about/#webpage\",\"url\":\"/about/\",\"name\":\"About | The PM Group\",\"isPartOf\":{\"@id\":\"/#website\"},\"datePublished\":\"2021-05-25T12:47:16+00:00\",\"dateModified\":\"2021-07-16T21:32:57+00:00\",\"breadcrumb\":{\"@id\":\"/about/#breadcrumb\"},\"inLanguage\":\"en-US\",\"potentialAction\":[{\"@type\":\"ReadAction\",\"target\":[\"/about/\"]}]},{\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"@id\":\"/about/#breadcrumb\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"About\"}]}]}"}},"aboutFields":{"aboutHero":{"aboutTitle":"What Makes The PM Group Different?","aboutBackgroundImage":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/95406a020749e4c7bc06537a2842e8d7/e9f4b/about-hero.png","srcSet":"/static/95406a020749e4c7bc06537a2842e8d7/46824/about-hero.png 480w,\n/static/95406a020749e4c7bc06537a2842e8d7/14612/about-hero.png 960w,\n/static/95406a020749e4c7bc06537a2842e8d7/e9f4b/about-hero.png 1920w","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/95406a020749e4c7bc06537a2842e8d7/9c6af/about-hero.webp 480w,\n/static/95406a020749e4c7bc06537a2842e8d7/0b22e/about-hero.webp 960w,\n/static/95406a020749e4c7bc06537a2842e8d7/a5663/about-hero.webp 1920w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw"}]},"width":1920,"height":800}}}}},"aboutGrid":{"aboutEntry":[{"content":"<p>Getting results is what matters most to us. We don&#8217;t have big artistic egos or like to waste time or money (yours or ours)! We&#8217;re here to make things happen. That’s why clients stay with us for decades.</p>\n","title":"Our Approach","icon":"moon"},{"content":"<p>We are flexible and we love what we do! We have both small project clients and contract clients with extensive marketing needs. We love them both.</p>\n","title":"We Love Clients Big and Small","icon":"moon"},{"content":"<p>The PM Group is the largest buyer of media in our region, with unsurpassed media strength, experience and resources. It’s funny how our competitors often ask the media for ‘The PM Group’ rates… only to be greatly disappointed that those rates aren’t available to agencies (and their clients) that don’t have the collective buying power of our agency.</p>\n","title":"Media Clout","icon":"moon"},{"content":"<p>You don’t become (and stay) the #1 advertising agency in San Antonio/South Texas for the last 20 years without a long history of client success. Ask us and we will share why clients stay with us so long when the industry average is just 4.5 years.</p>\n","title":"Our Track Record","icon":"moon"},{"content":"<p>Our in-house staff (NOT freelancers) from The PM Group and our constellation of companies allow us to control costs, hit deadlines and deliver high-level production values.</p>\n","title":"Streamlined In-House Production","icon":"moon"}]},"aboutTeamHero":{"aboutTeamHeroTitle":"Our Leadership Team","aboutTeamHeroImage":null},"aboutTeam":{"aboutImageRepeater":[{"teamJobTitle":null,"teamName":null,"teamLink":null,"te